        labelFor:"password",
        id:"password",
        name:"password",
        type:"password",
        autoComplete:"current-password",
        isRequired:true,
        placeholder:"Password"

]

    {
        labelText:"Password",

        autoComplete:"current-password",

        placeholder:"Password"

    {
        labelText:"Confirm Password",

    {
        labelText:"phone",

        isRequired:true,
        placeholder:"phone"
    },
]

export {loginFields, signupFields}
